      <div class="lwm-card">
        <div class="lwm-section">
          <div class="lwm-section-heading">
            <h2>Why people keep coming back to LiveWithMS</h2>
            <p>
              The app is not just a tracker. It becomes a daily support system that helps you remember, reflect, plan, and move through harder moments with more confidence.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="lwm-feature-grid">
            <article class="lwm-feature-card">
              <div class="lwm-feature-icon">01</div>
              <div class="lwm-feature-copy">
                <span class="lwm-feature-kicker">Daily check-ins</span>
                <h3>Capture how the day feels in under a minute.</h3>
                <p>Track energy, mood, stress, fatigue, sleep, hydration, and body signals without turning it into a long task.</p>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="lwm-feature-card">
              <div class="lwm-feature-icon">02</div>
              <div class="lwm-feature-copy">
                <span class="lwm-feature-kicker">Pattern insight</span>
                <h3>Notice what may be moving together.</h3>
                <p>Look for possible links between sleep, hydration, stress, symptoms, and energy using language that stays cautious and understandable.</p>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="lwm-feature-card">
              <div class="lwm-feature-icon">03</div>
              <div class="lwm-feature-copy">
                <span class="lwm-feature-kicker">AI-guided support</span>
                <h3>Get help organizing thoughts on difficult days.</h3>
                <p>Use Coach when you need to think through symptoms, appointments, meals, stress, or planning without staring at a blank page.</p>
              </div>
