                <span class="lwm-feature-kicker">Programs</span>
                <h3>Open the right tool for the moment you are in.</h3>
                <p>Reduce overwhelm, reset breathing, prepare for appointments, and use guided tools built for fatigue, pacing, and mental overload.</p>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="lwm-feature-card">
              <div class="lwm-feature-icon">06</div>
              <div class="lwm-feature-copy">
                <span class="lwm-feature-kicker">Brain games</span>
                <h3>Support focus, memory, and working attention gently.</h3>
                <p>Short exercises help create a steadier rhythm for attention and concentration without feeling childish or noisy.</p>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="lwm-feature-card">
              <div class="lwm-feature-icon">07</div>
              <div class="lwm-feature-copy">
